Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't let go of my hand, mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The man. ..was Czechoslovakian\Nof German decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the oldest son\Nof a family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that remained in Bohemia\Nafter the Second World War.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a soldier who graduated\Nfrom a military academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an elite, someone who was\Nto lead the country in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His name...\NHis name is not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was the only daughter of a\NMoravian elementary-school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a beautiful blonde-haired,\Nblue-eyed woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She went the University of Bruno.\NShe majored in genetic engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her teachers had\Ngreat expectations for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a talented woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name. ..\NHer name...is not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The two met at a cafe in Prague. It\Ndidn't take long for them to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after,\Nthe woman became pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man\Nmade a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"This was a mission"' he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He told her that there was\Nan experiment being conducted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,involving several dozen\Ncouples of men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen for their race, intellect, physique,\Nand athletic abilities to produce children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and that they were\None of those couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The man had followed\Nthe orders as planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said that he no longer\Nwanted to do so anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The man said that he wouldn't\Ndo things as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But his actions were\Nalready a part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman was isolated\Nin an unfamiliar room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me see him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been assigned\Na new mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me see him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been assigned\Na new mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me see him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been assigned\Na new mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let me see him.\NLet me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let me see him.\NLet me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew that he\Nwas no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Her unborn children grew well.\NThey were twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turn your head this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman began to realize that\Nthe man who came to visit often...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the man who was sketching her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was the man responsible\Nfor the whole experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.\NI will never forgive you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I die, the children who are\Ngrowing inside of me will get revenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You say the most\Ninteresting things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The due date came and\Nthe moment of birth had arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was being moved to a different\Nroom to calm her of her labor pains,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she finally sprang into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a several\Ndozen centimeters wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pregnant and wracked with labor pains,\Nshe escaped through a ventilation duct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She collapsed on the road several\Ndozen meters from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her water broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What beautiful children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So these children are the ones who\Nwill lead the future of the human race.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wonderful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought of names for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't need to think\Nof unnecessary things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought of names for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't need\Nto think about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Names...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give them names.\NGive them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all right.\NThey don't need names.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz.. .Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan asked me about\Nwhere he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Bonaparta alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"I won't forgive you.\NI will never forgive you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even if I die, the children who are\Ngrowing inside of me will get revenge."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta is still alive,\Nisn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should ask Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hospital up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there if you tell me\Nwhere Johan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,\Nyou're going to bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know\Nwhat I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You shoot me with a gun,\Nyou make me bleed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and you threaten me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us now! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.\NThere's a pay phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the hospital and tell them\Nthat there's an injured person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who's bleeding excessively\Nin this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?!\NHe's about to tell us where Johan's-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His life will be in danger\Nif we stall any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always like this.\NYou can't kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you where Johan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo, the hospital's sending\Nan ambulance right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get away from here\Nimmediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kenzo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He left a message for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't let you get involved\Nany further. I've ruined your life."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm very sorry.\NPlease find happiness"' he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}L-It's a fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Three Frogs is on fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat that quickly,\Nyou're going to choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have\Nbeen really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you two\Ncome from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't talk at all,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. We can talk once\Nyour stomachs are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have any parents,\Ndo they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they did, maybe there's\Na reason they don't want to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always\Nwanted children, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We could take them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't mean to be harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look. A pretty flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give it to\Nthe man and the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?\NI have a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When I escaped from\NRed Rose Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you greeted me when I got to\Nthe room at the Three Frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time,\NI'll say it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of time has passed since I came\Nfor you in Heidelberg on our 20th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fortners and\Nthe Lieberts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who had\Nbeen kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please come back to life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "Today's a nice day,\Nisn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you hurry a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all right.\NHang in there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to shoot me\Nlike you did then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to\Nput an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen the end of\Nthe world over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to die\Nand I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you seen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a truly terrifying story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm back.{\i0}
